subject: Pole Vault
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Yelena Isinbayeva broke her indoor world record in the women’s pole vault by clearing 16 feet 2 ¾ inches in Donetsk, Ukraine. Isinbayeva, a Russian, improved on her previous record of 16-2 that was set at this event last year.
